name: Rancor Mount
Lore: 'Indigenous to Dathomir, but found on several dozen worlds throughout the galaxy. Vicious predator. Sometimes kept as pets by eccentrics and crime lords.',
Text: 'May add a witch as ''rider'' (passenger).  Ability = 1/2.  While ridden by a Dathomir Witch, power +2, cannot be attacked, your Force drains here are +1, and vehicle and ''rider'' are immune to attrition < 4.',
